{"tid":2167445,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"從葉璇到「健康碼」 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-08-21T06:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T06:34:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"94a9495cf87974e89dda7639f4dc15a0df959f47","tid":2167445,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200821/QTRTTTYT75DOBC5N3BFXHGHKYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200821%2FQTRTTTYT75DOBC5N3BFXHGHKYI%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu1QKcmgIyYy1b1J%2Bn%2Bjwg5M%3D&h=54004d14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200821%2FQTRTTTYT75DOBC5N3BFXHGHKYI%2F&h=f6a4df63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200821/QTRTTTYT75DOBC5N3BFXHGHKYI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n從葉璇到「健康碼」 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UM7Yy9NnpAQgAzOwux29XvCDfwY=/6080x3178/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HQ3CJ6J62NGJPLMRHRVNQL2JVA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUM7Yy9NnpAQgAzOwux29XvCDfwY%3D%2F6080x3178%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHQ3CJ6J62NGJPLMRHRVNQL2JVA.JPG&h=97752f59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在說港版「健康碼」之前，我想先說說葉璇。<br />\n<br />\n幾年前，葉璇一宗緋聞引發的「社會信用評級」降級事件，令我印象非常深刻。<br />\n<br />\n當時，葉璇跟中國一個名叫「小默先生」的男人熱戀中。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n葉璇沒有理會。事件當然不會這樣結束。後來葉璇外遊，在機場被禁止上機、離境，她這才得知她已經成為「失去社會信用」的人。這意味着她無法乘坐高鐵、飛機，入住酒店，進行消費等等。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n當時我雖然同情她的處境，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中國從2014年開始，逐步建立「社會信用系統」，實施全民監控，許多被剝奪自由的人並非真的犯了法（犯法可以接受法律制裁），而只是政見不同。中國有意把香港和澳門納入這個監控系統，廣東省政府公佈的《粵港澳大灣區建設3年行動計劃（2018-2020年）》，便計劃3年內在粵、港、澳全面建構「社會信用評分」系統。<br />\n<br />\n這就是全民檢疫，設置港版「健康碼」的原因。"},{"pid":"a8dfaf100d4df6db7b9bfd6a0227d183dea5d1c1","tid":2167445,"uid":285165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccc89f106751038f7d3b89702bc3a87006c8e82f","tid":2167445,"uid":100542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94a9495cf87974e89dda7639f4dc15a0df959f47","tid":2167445,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:12:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200821/QTRTTTYT75DOBC5N3BFXHGHKYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200821%2FQTRTTTYT75DOBC5N3BFXHGHKYI%2F&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu1QKcmgIyYy1b1J%2Bn%2Bjwg5M%3D&h=54004d14\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200821%2FQTRTTTYT75DOBC5N3BFXHGHKYI%2F&h=f6a4df63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200821/QTRTTTYT75DOBC5N3BFXHGHKYI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n從葉璇到「健康碼」 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UM7Yy9NnpAQgAzOwux29XvCDfwY=/6080x3178/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HQ3CJ6J62NGJPLMRHRVNQL2JVA.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUM7Yy9NnpAQgAzOwux29XvCDfwY%3D%2F6080x3178%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHQ3CJ6J62NGJPLMRHRVNQL2JVA.JPG&h=97752f59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在說港版「健康碼」之前，我想先說說葉璇。<br />\n<br />\n幾年前，葉璇一宗緋聞引發的「社會信用評級」降級事件，令我印象非常深刻。<br />\n<br />\n當時，葉璇跟中國一個名叫「小默先生」的男人熱戀中。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n葉璇沒有理會。事件當然不會這樣結束。後來葉璇外遊，在機場被禁止上機、離境，她這才得知她已經成為「失去社會信用」的人。這意味着她無法乘坐高鐵、飛機，入住酒店，進行消費等等。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n當時我雖然同情她的處境，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中國從2014年開始，逐步建立「社會信用系統」，實施全民監控，許多被剝奪自由的人並非真的犯了法（犯法可以接受法律制裁），而只是政見不同。中國有意把香港和澳門納入這個監控系統，廣東省政府公佈的《粵港澳大灣區建設3年行動計劃（2018-2020年）》，便計劃3年內在粵、港、澳全面建構「社會信用評分」系統。<br />\n<br />\n這就是全民檢疫，設置港版「健康碼」的原因。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:15:20.000Z","msg":"所以葉旋而家咪搏晒命奶<br />\n二手飯都要笑住咗爭嚟食"},{"pid":"7b83eaf3612bb717127cca5a59bf48ff92c73727","tid":2167445,"uid":285165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fa9b0f915bc4fc19ed80874110935421c5b3c28","tid":2167445,"uid":285165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04990b958b45cf8f73f08164dc1f92b5ddf33a00","tid":2167445,"uid":180293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T06:34:32.000Z","msg":"跟住你串我呀嘛"}]}